Also some1 on diff posts always say something about changing the batch file thing with the java version you have i have java 6 update 25 version 6.0.260 and then java tm se development kit 6 version 1.6.0.0 which is the jdk version you need i justneed how to get all the compiler and stuff to work. Also i have windows 32 and in the edit part of the run and others it says (x86) wat do i do about that!
